Display clear.
KernelInstaller fileInClassChunks: 'RecorzKernelClass: #MethodBlockCaptureReporter superclass: #Object instanceVariableNames: ''value''
!
sum
    | x |
    x := 1.
    [ x := x + 2. x ] value.
    ^x
!'.
Transcript show: 'MCAP'.
Transcript cr.
Transcript show: (((KernelInstaller classNamed: 'MethodBlockCaptureReporter') new) sum printString).
Transcript cr.
